name: BlockTrader365
description: BlockTrader365 and its platform token $BT365 enables users to make better trading decisions by only providing the most valuable onchain data about a token and its holders behavior. The platform charges a small fee for conduction transactions, which is used for buying back the $BT365 token. By holding the $BT365 token users can gain access to valuable onchain data, and get a boosted point score on the trading leaderboard.
